Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)}A Gentle Snowfall of Remembrance
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, hey, hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? {He isn't here}He’s not up here?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's calling for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, this isn't good. Without thinking, I...}O-Oh, I couldn’t possibly show my face now.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough}I mean it! Come out already!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If you don't{} come out,\NI'm gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.06,0:00:35.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We're gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know where Usopp is, Sogeking?\NI can't find him anywhere!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.99,0:00:45.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry.\N{He went back ahead of us on a small boat earlier.}He departed on a small boat, just before we did.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But this ship actually belongs to him now.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just what is it they need in \Norder to recognize Usopp?}How the hell do they not recognize that he’s Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Not here, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As we suspected, I can't find anyone anywhere on this ship.}It’s as we thought.\NThere isn’t anyone anywhere on this ship.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder who on earth sailed this ship to us...}I wonder who could’ve sailed this ship to us.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we definitely heard that \Nvoice calling out to us.}But we all heard the same voice calling out to us.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}You did?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yes, someone most certainly called to us.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.14,0:01:28.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said all this time... \Nit was the Merry's voice!}Like I’ve been saying,\Nit was the Merry's voice!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.40,0:01:31.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.57,0:01:36.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Right, Merry?! Say something!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You idiot. There's no way a ship {w}could talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.80,0:01:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I kinda felt that way too, though...}I kinda felt that way at first,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.11,0:01:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But there's no way something like that... could happen, huh?}but something like that should be impossible, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see a ship coming towards us!}There’s a ship heading toward us!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Who's that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.74,0:02:07.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So you guys're okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Galley-La Company's ship...}A Galley-La Company ship?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They rushed out in Aqua Laguna and still made it okay! I can't believe it!}They rushed out in the middle of Aqua Laguna\Nand still made it okay! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They came back from Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahoy{!}, Ice{ pops}boss!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stupid-burg.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What a crazy bunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They took on the World Government...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,and {they }really {took}got everything back.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look! Their ship{ is...}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?!\NWhat happened all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden? Isn't {this just}it only natural?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was declared that Merry could no longer sail.}The Merry was declared unfit for the seas.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But{...}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The }Merry{ is...}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pops}Boss! This is bad! Merry is in trouble!\N{Please}You gotta do something!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys... This is good timing! You guys're all shipwrights, right?!}You guys, this is great timing!\NYou're all shipwrights, right?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you! Please do something!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's our friend who has been traveling with us all this time!}She's our friend and has traveled with us for so long!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And just a bit ago she saved us!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So please, {pops}boss!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then let her...}Then allow her...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{}to rest now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've already done everything I could.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.57,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What's {this}that sound?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Is someone on Scrap Island?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.47,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Isn't this{...} the Straw Hats' ship?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.38,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The damage must've been caused by Aqua Laguna. It's in a terrible state.}The damage from Aqua Laguna left her in bad shape.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.88,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Well, I guess it's beyond just damage...}No, she was like this before the storm.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.84,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,I want to set sail.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.06,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,I want to set sail one last time!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.27,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.51,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,There's no hope left for this ship.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.18,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Iceburg-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.73,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?!\NAnother big wave is coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.62,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.09,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What?! You want to set sail?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.05,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The sea is still stormy!}The storm hasn’t let up yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,I'll go alone if I have to.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We can't let you go out there all by yourself!}Then we can't let you go out there all by yourself!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm {watching}witnessing a miracle right now{...}:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A miracle of a ship that has long passed its limits...}The miracle of a ship \Nthat has long passed its limits.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been a shipwright for many years,}In all my years as a shipwright,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I've never seen \Na pirate ship this incredible.}I've never seen a pirate ship this remarkable.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's lived a splendid life.}She's lived a splendid life.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.97,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Let's go back, everyone!}Everyone, let’s go back!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.91,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Back to the seas of adventure!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.15,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,I came to get you!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay...}I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, then... are you guys ready?}Well then, are you guys ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Merry... the seabed is dark and lonesome,}Merry, the seabed is dark and lonesome,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so we'll watch you to the end.}so we’ll see you off to the very end.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maybe it{ was good}'s for the best that Usopp {was}isn't here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way... that he could bear this.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Any thoughts?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Everyone must someday say farewell.\NThis is a man's parting.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not even a single tear should be shed.}I mustn’t shed a single tear.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He, too... is prepared.}So he, too, is prepared.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.15,0:09:44.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for carrying us for \Nsuch a long time, Merry.}You carried us for so long.\NThank you, Merry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Snow{...}!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,A caravel!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.63,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.46,0:10:20.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Now the pirate ship,\Nthe Going Merry, is complete!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Cheers to our new ship and crewmate!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Look at this! \NThe Merry got damaged quite a bit!}Look at this!\NThe Merry took quite a bit of damage!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.24,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{When navigating a sailboat, \Neveryone has to participate!}When operating a ship with sails,\Neveryone needs to do their part!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Learn it appropriately!}You need to remember that!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.37,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Ih'm shorree.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.43,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?!}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.52,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Cannon practice!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.25,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,They sure don't fly{} too good!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, let me try!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.92,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Awesome! You hit it on your first try!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.64,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Whoa{...}! I really hit it on my first try!
