Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The entrance to the Grand Line \Nlies ahead of that light.}The entrance to the Grand Line\Nlies just beyond that light.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.12,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}To find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}To be king of the pirates!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.79,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}To become the greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}To draw a world map!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.00,0:11:43.26,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}T-To become a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.66,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We're going...}On to the Grand Line!{!}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,The entrance to the Grand Line is a mountain!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.68,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest sea in the world!
